# Project Structure Rules

## Directory Organization

### Root Structure
```
frontend-main/
├── .cursor/              # Cursor rules
├── public/               # Static assets
├── src/
│   ├── assets/          # Images, icons, etc.
│   ├── components/      # Reusable components
│   ├── config/          # Configuration files
│   ├── hooks/           # Custom React hooks
│   ├── lib/             # Utility functions
│   ├── navigation/      # Routing configuration
│   ├── pages/           # Page components
│   ├── redux/           # Redux store and slices
│   ├── services/        # API services
│   └── styles/          # Global styles
├── components.json      # shadcn/ui config
├── package.json
└── vite.config.js
```

## Source Directory Structure

### Components (`src/components/`)
```
components/
├── ui/                  # shadcn/ui components
├── Layout/             # Layout components
├── ErrorBoundary/      # Error boundary component
├── Loader/             # Loading components
├── multi-select.jsx    # Multi-select component
└── index.js           # Component exports
```

### Pages (`src/pages/`)
```
pages/
├── Home/
│   ├── index.jsx
│   └── components/     # Page-specific components 
│       └── HomeCard.jsx
├── Login/
│   ├── index.jsx
│   └── components/     # Page-specific components 
│       └── LoginForm.jsx
└── NotFound/
    └── index.jsx
```

### Page Structure Pattern
- Each page can have its own `components/` folder for page-specific components
- Page-specific components are only used within that page
- Reusable components should be in `src/components/` instead
- Use `components/` folder when a component is tightly coupled to the page

### Redux (`src/redux/`)
```
redux/
├── actions/           # Action creators
│   └── sessionActions.js
├── reducer/           # Redux slices
│   ├── index.js
│   └── sessionReducer.js
├── store/             # Store configuration
│   └── index.ts
├── hooks.js          # Typed Redux hooks
└── index.js          # Redux exports
```

### Services (`src/services/`)
```
services/
├── apis/              # API modules
│   ├── auth.js
│   └── user-management/
│       └── index.js
├── core.js           # Axios setup, interceptors
└── index.js          # Service exports
```

### Hooks (`src/hooks/`)
```
hooks/
├── use-mobile.js
├── useTheme.jsx
├── useErrorLog/
│   └── index.jsx
└── index.js          # Hook exports
```

## File Naming Conventions

### Components
- Use PascalCase: `ComponentName.jsx`
- Main component file: `index.jsx` (in component folder)
- Sub-components: `component-name.jsx`

### Utilities
- Use camelCase: `utilityName.js`
- Constants: `CONSTANT_NAME.js` or in config

### Pages
- Use PascalCase folder: `PageName/`
- Main file: `index.jsx`

