## Component Organization

### Component Folder Structure
```
ComponentName/
├── index.jsx          # Main component (default export)
├── components/        # Sub-components (if needed)
│   └── SubComponent.jsx
└── hooks/            # Component-specific hooks (if needed)
    └── useComponentHook.js
```

### Export Pattern
```javascript
// Component file
export default ComponentName;

// Index file (src/components/index.js)
export { default as ComponentName } from './ComponentName';
export { default as Loader } from './Loader';
```

## File Organization Rules

### DO
- Group related files in folders
- Use `index.jsx` for main component files
- Export from index files for clean imports
- Keep components small and focused
- Separate concerns (UI, logic, data)

### DON'T
- Don't create deep nesting (max 3-4 levels)
- Don't mix concerns in single files
- Don't use absolute paths without aliases
- Don't create circular dependencies

